    "100304": {
        "Desc": "Ask the boss lady about Xiao",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Tell me about that adeptus"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "Oh? You've already met Xiao?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "Not bad. Not often he's in a good enough mood to agree to see people."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's his good mood?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "Oh yes, the adepti are very hard to come by. Many people go their whole lives praying to them, never once actually getting to see one."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "When the Geo Archon built Liyue, he borrowed power from the adepti."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "But most of them only know how to protect Liyue by fighting."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "So for many millennia, it has instead been humans who have led Liyue, whilst the adepti have lived hidden away on the outskirts."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You really know a lot, huh boss lady."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "It's not \"boss lady,\" it's just boss..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "Anyway, seen as you have the favor of the adepti, things should be a lot easier."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "Well... If you wanna know my opinion... If you keep Xiao in a good mood, things should be okay."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Good mood? Can't really imagine what a \"good mood\" looks like for that \"Vigilant Yaksha.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "Haha! Will be interesting, won't it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "(Come to think of it, I've never seen him smile either...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "How 'bout this — you go see the chef for a bowl of Almond Tofu, and a plate of whatever it is you are best at making."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Verr Goldet",
                    "T": "Almond Tofu is one of the few human foods Xiao likes. The other dish is up to you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Up to us, eh...? {NICKNAME}, what do you think you're the best at cooking?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Satisfying Salad I guess?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Really hard to screw that one up, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Perhaps a Maha Manjusaka Hot Pyro Slime?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow! Never heard of that one! Paimon wants to try it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But, if we're gonna be cooking for an adeptus, perhaps the Satisfying Salad would be the safer choice..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
