    "100306": {
        "Desc": "Talk to the chef",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Smiley Yanxiao",
                    "T": "Can't you see I'm on a break kid? Scram."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Excuse me, we'd like an Almond To—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Smiley Yanxiao",
                    "T": "Scram!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa, this chef guy's service is about as good as that Wagner guy's back in Mondstadt."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's for the boss, Goldet."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Smiley Yanxiao",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Smiley Yanxiao",
                    "T": "I see. If it's for the boss, then guess I don't have a choice now, do I?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Smiley Yanxiao",
                    "T": "But my heart's not really in it right now, not enough to make a dessert as painstaking as Almond Tofu."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And why is that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Smiley Yanxiao",
                    "T": "A fencer's hand must be steady, so too must the hand of a chef."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Smiley Yanxiao",
                    "T": "But my hands, I'm... they're not steady..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Smiley Yanxiao",
                    "T": "Because ahh, a traveler once told me that this inn... is haunted."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Smiley Yanxiao",
                    "T": "And then, just now — just now! In the kitchen... I saw something... something not right."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "(This chef looks so intimidating, but speak of ghosts and he becomes weak.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Smiley Yanxiao",
                    "T": "I keep thinking... even Wangshu Inn isn't safe. I—I can't keep a steady hand for something like Almond Tofu."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Alright {NICKNAME}. In the name of high-quality Almond Tofu, we need to go check this kitchen out."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
